{{<description>}}
The Foo Fighters are one of the greatest bands in rock music. Born from the ashes of Nirvana, Foo Fighters have gone on to take their own place in rock history. These are the songs that I think are the <em>best</em> from their repertoire.
{{</description>}}

{{<fullimage src="https://cdn.ryanparman.com/hugo/posts/2019/foo-fighters@2x.jpg" alt="Foo Fighters">}}

## Playlist

{{< apple-music "https://embed.music.apple.com/us/playlist/best-of-foo-fighters/pl.u-bxvN3TJL6v8?app=music" "album" >}}

